Underneath the silver of the midnight moon
[chorus]
Life is like a jazz improvisation
Filling moments with pure sensation
In the blues we find our true salvation
Music heals the pain of separation
[bridge]
[verse]
Dim lights and smoke create a magic atmosphere
The bass line groove is all we want to hear
Improvisation takes us far away
In this jazz paradise we want to stay
